citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:20 pm on 27-OCT-
21. The inspector made a phone call to the licensee and left a message. Contact was made shortly thereafter and no
responsible adult would be available for inspection within 60 minutes.
End Section
